npx create-react-app hardware-website
cd hardware-website

npm install react-router-dom

file structure::

src/
  components/
    Header.js
    Footer.js
  pages/
    Home.js
    Products.js
    ProductDetails.js
    About.js
    Contact.js
    Admin.js
  App.js
  index.js

To run your app, use:

npm start
